{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"java.io"},"Provides for system input and output through data streams, serialization and the file system. Unless otherwise noted, passing a null argument to a constructor or method in any class or interface in this package will cause a NullPointerException to be thrown.\r\n\r\n## Package Specification ##\r\n\r\n *   Java Object Serialization Specification \r\n\r\n## Related Documentation ##\r\n\r\nFor overviews, tutorials, examples, guides, and tool documentation, please see:\r\n\r\n *  Serialization Enhancements\r\n\r\nSince:\r\n\r\nJDK1.0"]},"id":"143","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
