{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"javax.validation"},"Top level package of the Bean Validation API. The main runtime artifacts are:\r\n\r\n *  javax.validation.Validation: the entry point to bootstrap Bean Validation\r\n *  javax.validation.ValidatorFactory: the bootstrapped Bean Validation engine\r\n *  javax.validation.Validator: contract to validate beans and access the metadata\r\n *  javax.validation.ConstraintViolation: constraint violation report\r\n\r\nThe main constraint definition artifacts are:\r\n\r\n *  javax.validation.Constraint: annotation marking an annotation as being a constraint\r\n *  javax.validation.ConstraintValidator: interface implemented by the piece of code validating a given constraint\r\n *  javax.validation.ReportAsSingleViolation: marks a composed constraint as returning a single constraint violation report\r\n\r\nThe main constraint declaration artifacts are:\r\n\r\n *  javax.validation.Valid: annotation marking an association as cascaded during validation\r\n *  javax.validation.GroupSequence: defines a sequence of groups that should be validated sequentially"]},"id":"1229","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
