{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"javax.persistence.CascadeType"},"Defines the set of cascadable operations that are propagated to the associated entity. The value `cascade\u003dALL` is equivalent to `cascade\u003d{PERSIST, MERGE, REMOVE, REFRESH, DETACH}`.\r\n\r\n *  **Since:**\r\n    \r\n     *  Java Persistence 1.0"]},"id":"1377","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
