{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"org.springframework.ui.ModelMap"},"Implementation of java.util.Map for use when building model data for use with UI tools. Supports chained calls and generation of model attribute names.\r\n\r\nThis class serves as generic model holder for Servlet MVC but is not tied to it. Check out the Model interface for an interface variant.\r\n\r\n *  **Since:**\r\n    \r\n     *  2.0\r\n *  **Author:**\r\n    \r\n     *  Rob Harrop\r\n    \r\n     *  Juergen Hoeller\r\n *  **See Also:**\r\n    \r\n     *  Conventions.getVariableName\r\n    \r\n     *  org.springframework.web.servlet.ModelAndView"]},"id":"1910","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
