{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.PathVariable"},"Annotation which indicates that a method parameter should be bound to a URI template variable. Supported for RequestMapping annotated handler methods.\r\n\r\nIf the method parameter is Map\u003cString, String\u003e then the map is populated with all path variable names and values.\r\n\r\n *  **Since:**\r\n    \r\n     *  3.0\r\n *  **Author:**\r\n    \r\n     *  Arjen Poutsma\r\n    \r\n     *  Juergen Hoeller\r\n *  **See Also:**\r\n    \r\n     *  RequestMapping\r\n    \r\n     *  org.springframework.web.servlet.mvc.method.annotation.RequestMappingHandlerAdapter"]},"id":"1912","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
