{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"org.springframework.util.StringUtils"},"Miscellaneous String utility methods.\r\n\r\nMainly for internal use within the framework; consider [Apache\u0027s Commons Lang](https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/) for a more comprehensive suite of `String` utilities.\r\n\r\nThis class delivers some simple functionality that should really be provided by the core Java String and StringBuilder classes. It also provides easy-to-use methods to convert between delimited strings, such as CSV strings, and collections and arrays.\r\n\r\n *  **Since:**\r\n    \r\n     *  16 April 2001\r\n *  **Author:**\r\n    \r\n     *  Rod Johnson\r\n    \r\n     *  Juergen Hoeller\r\n    \r\n     *  Keith Donald\r\n    \r\n     *  Rob Harrop\r\n    \r\n     *  Rick Evans\r\n    \r\n     *  Arjen Poutsma\r\n    \r\n     *  Sam Brannen\r\n    \r\n     *  Brian Clozel"]},"id":"2130","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
