{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.PostMapping"},"Annotation for mapping HTTP `POST` requests onto specific handler methods.\r\n\r\nSpecifically, `@PostMapping` is a *composed annotation* that acts as a shortcut for `@RequestMapping(method \u003d RequestMethod.POST)`.\r\n\r\n *  **Since:**\r\n    \r\n     *  4.3\r\n *  **Author:**\r\n    \r\n     *  Sam Brannen\r\n *  **See Also:**\r\n    \r\n     *  GetMapping\r\n    \r\n     *  PutMapping\r\n    \r\n     *  DeleteMapping\r\n    \r\n     *  PatchMapping\r\n    \r\n     *  RequestMapping"]},"id":"2225","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
