{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"org.springframework.beans.support.PropertyComparator"},"PropertyComparator performs a comparison of two beans, evaluating the specified bean property via a BeanWrapper.\r\n\r\n *  **Type Parameters:**\r\n    \r\n     *  **\u003cT\u003e** the type of objects that may be compared by this comparator\r\n *  **Since:**\r\n    \r\n     *  19.05.2003\r\n *  **Author:**\r\n    \r\n     *  Juergen Hoeller\r\n    \r\n     *  Jean-Pierre Pawlak\r\n *  **See Also:**\r\n    \r\n     *  org.springframework.beans.BeanWrapper"]},"id":"2541","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
