{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"AbstractStringAssert\u003cObject\u003e org.assertj.core.api.AbstractAssert.isEqualTo(Object expected)"},"Verifies that the actual value is equal to the given one.\r\n\r\nExample:\r\n\r\n    // assertions will pass\n     assertThat(\"abc\").isEqualTo(\"abc\");\n     assertThat(new HashMap\u003cString, Integer\u003e()).isEqualTo(new HashMap\u003cString, Integer\u003e());\n    \n     // assertions will fail\n     assertThat(\"abc\").isEqualTo(\"123\");\n     assertThat(new ArrayList\u003cString\u003e()).isEqualTo(1);\r\n\r\n *  **Parameters:**\r\n    \r\n     *  expected\r\n *  **Returns:**\r\n    \r\n     *  `this` assertion object."]},"id":"11272","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
