{"result":{"contents":[{"language":"java","value":"AbstractLongAssert\u003cObject\u003e org.assertj.core.api.AbstractLongAssert.isNotEqualTo(long other)"},"Verifies that the actual value is not equal to the given one.\r\n\r\nExample:\r\n\r\n    // assertions will pass:\n     assertThat(1L).isNotEqualTo(2L);\n     assertThat(1L).isNotEqualTo(-1L);\n     \n     // assertion will fail:\n     assertThat(1L).isNotEqualTo(1L);\r\n\r\n *  **Parameters:**\r\n    \r\n     *  **other** the given value to compare the actual value to.\r\n *  **Returns:**\r\n    \r\n     *  `this` assertion object.\r\n *  **Throws:**\r\n    \r\n     *  AssertionError \\- if the actual value is `null`.\r\n     *  AssertionError \\- if the actual value is equal to the given one."]},"id":"16441","type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult"}
